      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4 rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-6 text-slate-700">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-brand-50 p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-brand-700">How we help</p>
        <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7">
          <li>Claims denial management & appeals.</li>
          <li>Revenue cycle optimization for physician groups.</li>
          <li>Coding audits aligned with payer compliance.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Higher first-pass acceptance</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Reduce rejected claims with smarter ICD and CPT workflows.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Faster reimbursement</p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">Improve cash flow with best-practice billing review and denial appeals.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
